    "content": "The following table shows the target hardware for the application projects. | Project Name | Board | . | pic32ck_gc01_cult.X | PIC32CK GC01 Curiosity Ultra board | . |   |   | . Setting up PIC32CK GC01 Curiosity Ultra board . | Short RTC Input pin (EXT1, PIN 13) to Vcc | Connect the Debug USB port on the board to the computer using a micro USB cable | . ",
